description: Another day. Another appointment. Another guy who lost his job. When I came there I met a strong man in his early 30s who tried to appear as cool as he could. He had a nice apartment which was well-furnished. Believe me - his standard of living was above the average. Well, as I said - it was. He should have called for help earlier. His debts already started to mountain up. And the longer I talked to him the less he was able to hide his desperation behind his impressive manhood. You know that I am always careful when I meet muscle guys. You never know how they will react. I still decided to offer my conditions.
title: Debt Dandy 20
